sorry it took forever for me to update!ive been soo busy!i had the play at my school rebel w/out a cause, which i was in, only an adult extra, but w/e ill take what i can get. anyways i just wish aubrey would get ungrounded so we can hang out! i miss you b! well today has been great, exciting, weird, boring, akward, frustrating, and basically how life is and should be. and im tired as hell. so maybe i should get some rest, but ill right more in tommorows entry i promise. until tommorow, for real!

MN4LIFE!!!!!

Wow today was a roller coaster of emotions!i woke up great, felt like crap, went back to feeling good again and then again down in the dirt, but now im just neautral i guess. probably because im soo tired. i just pray to god for highschool to end. i hate feeling like i have to please everyone except for myself.well you cant get anywhere in life feeling sorry for yourself so i guess ill have to get over it. well thank god its the weekend tommorow! i get to go see sebastian bach in jekyll and hyde:) yessssss
well thats all for now:) until tommorow,
*Linds
